[
  // ==== ABILITIES ====
  // Soulknife
  {
    "Key": "ShapeMindBladeAbility.Name",
    "ProcessTemplates": false,
    "enGB_Base": "Shape Mind Blade",
    "zhCN": "灵刃变形"
  },
  {
    "Key": "ShapeMindBladeAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "As a Standard Action, change the shape of your mind blade.",
    "zhCN": "用一个标准动作，改变灵刃的形状。"
  },
  // Variants
  {
    "Key": "FormMindBladeAbility.Name",
    "ProcessTemplates": false,
    "enGB_Base": "Form Mind Blade",
    "zhCN": "灵刃塑形"
  },
  {
    "Key": "FormMindBladeAbility.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "As a move action, a soulknife can form a semi-solid weapon composed of psychic energy distilled from her own mind.\nA soulknife must choose the form of her mind blade at 1st level. She can either form it into a light weapon, a one-handed weapon, or a two-handed weapon. Once chosen, her mind blade stays in this form every time the soulknife forms her mind blade. The light weapon deals 1d6 points of damage, the one-handed weapon deals 1d8 points of damage, and the two-handed weapon deals 2d6 points of damage. All damages are based on a Medium-sized creature wielding Medium-sized weapons; adjust the weapon damage as appropriate for different sized weapons. In all forms, the mind blade has a critical range of 19-20/x2. A soulknife with powerful build or any similar ability forms an appropriately-sized mind blade dealing the size-appropriate amount of damage. If the soulknife’s chosen form is a light weapon, she may choose to form two light weapons when forming her mind blade if she so chooses, but she suffers the standard penalties for two-weapon fighting.\nRegardless of the weapon form a soulknife has chosen, her mind blade does not have a set damage type. When shaping her weapon and assigning abilities to it, the soulknife chooses whether it will deal bludgeoning, piercing, or slashing damage. The soulknife may change the damage type of an existing mind blade, or may summon a new mind blade with a different damage type, as a full-round action; otherwise, the mind blade retains the last damage type chosen every time it is summoned.\nThe blade can be broken (it has hardness 10 and 10 hit points); however, a soulknife can simply create another on her next move action. The moment she relinquishes her grip on her blade, it dissipates (unless she intends to throw it; see below). A mind blade is considered a magic weapon for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction and is considered a masterwork weapon.\nA soulknife can use feats such as Power Attack or Combat Expertise in conjunction with the mind blade just as if it were a normal weapon. She can also choose her mind blade for feats requiring a specific weapon choice, such as Weapon Focus and Improved Critical. Powers or spells that upgrade weapons can be used on a mind blade. The soulknife can use feats such as Weapon Finesse that work on light weapons with her mind blade, but such feats only work on mind blades in a light weapon form.\nEven in places where psionic effects do not normally function (such as within a null psionics field), a soulknife can attempt to sustain her mind blade by making a DC 20 Will save. On a successful save, the soulknife maintains her mind blade for a number of rounds equal to her class level before she needs to check again, although the mind blade is treated for all purposes as a non-magical, masterwork weapon while in a place where psionic effects do not normally function. On an unsuccessful attempt, the mind blade vanishes. As a move action on her turn, the soulknife can attempt a new Will save to rematerialize her mind blade while she remains within the psionics-negating effect. She gains a bonus on Will saves made to maintain or form her mind blade equal to the total enhancement bonus of her mind blade (see below).\nThe soulknife chooses the appearance of her mind blade, although its shape must reflect the selections the soulknife has chosen: a bludgeoning mind blade would be blunt, slashing would have an edge, etc.",
    "zhCN": "以一个移动动作，魂刃可以以灵能塑形出一把由她思想铸造的半固态灵刃\n魂刃必须在1级决定灵刃的形态．她可以选择将之塑形为一件轻型武器，一把单手武器，亦或是双手武器。一旦决定了造型，以后当她塑形灵刃时她的灵刃都会以这一形态出现。轻型武器形态可以造成1d6点伤害，单手武器形态可以造成1d8点伤害，双手武器可以造成2d6点伤害。以上的所有伤害都是以中型生物挥舞的中型武器计算的，根据不同的体型大小调整你的武器伤害。不论是哪一种形态，灵刃的重击范围都是19-20/X2。如果你的魂刃是大体型生物或是小体型生物，你可以根据她的体型来调整灵刃的伤害骰。如果魂刃选择将她的灵刃塑形为轻型武器，那她可以选择在显形灵刃时显现2把轻型武器造型的灵刃。如果她这么做的话她承受标准的双武减值。\n不论魂刃以何种形态塑形她的灵刃，灵刃本身并没有固定的伤害类型。当她显形灵刃并向其中灌注能量时，魂刃可以选择这把灵刃造成的伤害类型，钝击，挥砍，亦或是穿刺。以一个整轮动作，魂刃可以改变她现有灵刃的伤害类型或者重新显形一把不同伤害类型的灵刃。如果不这么做的话，灵刃会一直保持上一次显形时的伤害类型。\n灵刃可以被击碎（它的硬度为10并且有10点生命值），但魂刃可以用他的下一个移动等效动作重铸造一把。当魂刃松开了她紧握的灵刃时，这把灵刃会即时消散（除非她这么做是为了抛掷灵刃，详情见下文）。一把灵刃在计算DR时被视为魔法武器，同时被视为精制武器。\n如同普通武器一样，魂刃可以对灵刃应用“猛力攻击”，“寓守于攻”专长。此外，她也可以选择灵刃作为特殊专长的需求，比如武器专攻和精通重击。强化武器的灵能和法术也可以对灵刃起效。武器娴熟也可对灵刃生效，当然前提条件是这位魂刃的灵刃属于轻型武器形态。\n即使在灵能无法正常作用的地方（比如位于“反灵能力场”内），通过一个20dc的意志检定，魂刃依然可以制造并维持灵刃，通过这一方法显形的灵刃维持等于她魂刃职业等级的轮数。当持续时间结束后，她可以通过另一个20dc的意志检定维持她的灵刃，同时，在灵能无法正常作用地区，灵刃被视为非魔法武器及非精制武器。如果她未能成功通过这一意志检定，那她的灵刃将即时消散。于灵能无效地区，在她自己的行动回合内，魂刃可以通过一个新的意志检定（dc20）以一个移动动作重塑灵刃。她在这个意志检定上获得等同于灵刃增强加值的增强加值（灵刃增强加值见下）。\n魂刃可以决定她的灵刃造型，当然这一造型必须符合灵刃的伤害类型，比如钝击伤害类型的灵刃必须是钝器，挥砍伤害的灵刃必须有刃口，诸如此类。"
  },


