    "enGB_Base": "You create ectoplasmic crossbow bolts, arrows, or sling bullets, appropriate to your size, which dissipate into their constituent ectoplasmic particles when the duration ends. Ammunition you create has a +1 enhancement bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls.",
    "zhCN": "你可以创造符合你体形的灵质弩矢、箭或投石索弹药，当持续时间结束时，这些子弹会消散回灵子状态。你制造的灵能弹药在攻击和伤害骰上有+1增强加值。"
