    "enGB_Base": "Your shield of insight alerts you to potential dangers and supercharges your reaction time. You gain a +1 insight bonus on your Initiative checks for the duration of the effect.",
    "zhCN": "你的洞察之盾会提醒你潜在的危险，并增加你的反应时间。在效果持续时间内，你在先攻上获得+1洞察加值。"
