  {
    "Key": "DecelerationBuff.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You warp space around an individual, hindering the subject’s ability to move. The subject’s speed (in any movement mode it possesses) is halved. A subsequent manifestation of deceleration on the subject does not further decrease its speed.",
    "zhCN": "你扭曲了目标个体周围的空间，阻碍其移动能力。目标的速度（在其拥有的任何运动模式下）减半。目标减速后的行动不会进一步降低其速度。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EctoplasmicSheenBuff.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Ectoplasmic Sheen",
    "zhCN": "灵质光彩"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EctoplasmicSheenBuff.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You draw forth ectoplasm in an area, causing the surface to become slick. Any creature in the area when the power is manifested must make a successful Reflex save or fall. A creature can walk within or through the area of ectoplasm at half normal speed with a DC 10 Acrobatics check. Failure means it can’t move that round (and must then make a Reflex save or fall), while failure by 5 or more means it falls (see the Acrobatics skill for details). Creatures that do not move on their turn do not need to make this check and are not considered flat-footed.",
    "zhCN": "你在一个区域中覆盖灵质，使其表面变得光滑。显能时，该区域内的任何生物都必须成功进行反射豁免来避免摔倒。通过DC 10的灵巧检定可以让生物以减半速度在灵质区域内行走或穿过灵质区域。失败则意味着那一轮不能移动（然后必须进行反射豁免避免摔倒），而失败超过5点以上意味着摔倒（详见灵巧技能）。在自己回合没有进行移动的生物不需要进行该检定，也不被视为措手不及。"
  },
