    "enGB_Base": "You create ectoplasmic crossbow bolts, arrows, or sling bullets, appropriate to your size, which dissipate into their constituent ectoplasmic particles when the duration ends. Ammunition you create has a +1 enhancement bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls.\nAugment For every 3 additional power points you spend, this power improves the ammunition’s enhancement bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls by 1",
