    "Key": "DecelerationPower.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You warp space around an individual, hindering the subject’s ability to move. The subject’s speed (in any movement mode it possesses) is halved. A subsequent manifestation of deceleration on the subject does not further decrease its speed.\nAugment For every 2 additional power points you spend, this power’s save DC increases by 1",
    "zhCN": "你扭曲了目标个体周围的空间，阻碍其移动能力。目标的速度（在其拥有的任何运动模式下）减半。目标减速后的行动不会进一步降低其速度。\n每额外消耗2灵能点，该能力豁免DC增加1。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DemoralizePower.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Demoralize",
    "zhCN": "打击士气"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DemoralizePower.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You fill your enemies with self-doubt. Any enemy in the area that fails its save becomes shaken for the duration of the power. Allies and creatures without an Intelligence score are unaffected.",
    "zhCN": "你让你的敌人充满自我怀疑。该区域内任何未通过豁免的敌人都会在力量持续时间内陷入战栗。没有智力的生物和盟友不受影响。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DissipatingTouch.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Dissipating Touch",
    "zhCN": "消散之触"
  },
  {
    "Key": "DissipatingTouch.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "Your mere touch can disperse the surface material of a foe or object, sending a tiny portion of it far away. This effect is disruptive; thus, your successful melee touch attack deals 1d6 points of damage.\nAugment For every additional power point you spend, this power’s damage increases by 1d6 points.",
    "zhCN": "您只需触摸即可驱散敌人或物体的表层物质，将其一小部分送至远处。这种影响是破坏性的；因此，你成功的近战接触攻击会造成 1d6 点伤害。\n每额外消耗1灵能点，该能力的伤害就会增加 1d6 点。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EctoplasmicSheen.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Ectoplasmic Sheen",
    "zhCN": "灵质光彩"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EctoplasmicSheen.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You draw forth ectoplasm in an area, causing the surface to become slick. Any creature in the area when the power is manifested must make a successful Reflex save or fall. A creature can walk within or through the area of ectoplasm at half normal speed with a DC 10 Acrobatics check. Failure means it can’t move that round (and must then make a Reflex save or fall), while failure by 5 or more means it falls (see the Acrobatics skill for details). Creatures that do not move on their turn do not need to make this check and are not considered flat-footed.\nAugment For every two additional power points you spend augmenting this power, the power’s save DC increases by 1.",
    "zhCN": "你在一个区域中覆盖灵质，使其表面变得光滑。显能时，该区域内的任何生物都必须成功进行反射豁免来避免摔倒。通过DC 10的灵巧检定可以让生物以减半速度在灵质区域内行走或穿过灵质区域。失败则意味着那一轮不能移动（然后必须进行反射豁免避免摔倒），而失败超过5点以上意味着摔倒（详见灵巧技能）。在自己回合没有进行移动的生物不需要进行该检定，也不被视为措手不及。\n每额外消耗2灵能点，该能力的豁免DC就会增加1。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EnergyRay.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Energy Ray",
    "zhCN": "能量射线"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EnergyRay.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You create a ray of energy of your active energy type (cold, electricity, fire, or sonic) that shoots forth from your fingertip and strikes a target within range, dealing 1d6 points of damage, if you succeed on a ranged touch attack with the ray.\n<b>Cold</b> A ray of this energy type deals +1 point of damage per die.\n<b>Electricity</b> Manifesting a ray of this energy type provides a +3 bonus on your attack roll if the target is wearing metal armor and a +2 bonus on manifester level checks for the purpose of overcoming power resistance.\n<b>Fire</b> A ray of this energy type deals +1 point of damage per die.\n<b>Sonic</b> A ray of this energy type deals –1 point of damage per die and ignores an object’s hardness. This power’s subtype is the same as the type of energy you manifest.\nAugment You can augment this power in one of the following ways. 1. For every additional power point you spend, this power’s damage increases by one die (d6).\n 2. If you expend your psionic focus when manifesting this power, the cost of the power is reduced by 1 (to a minimum of 0), but the damage is reduced to 1d3 and it cannot be further augmented.",
    "zhCN": "你会产生一束由你激活的能量类型（寒冷、电击、火焰或声波）的射线，从指尖射出，击中射程内一个的目标，如果成功进行远程接触攻击造成1d6点伤害。\n每额外消耗2灵能点，该能力的豁免DC就会增加1。\n<b>寒冷：</b>这种射线造成每个伤害骰+1伤害。\n<b>电击：</b>在试图穿透法术抗力时在显能等级上获得+2加值，并且在目标穿着重甲时在攻击检定上获得+3加值。\n<b>火焰：</b>这种射线造成每个伤害骰+1伤害。\n<b>音波：</b>这种射线每个伤害骰-1伤害且无视目标硬度。该能力的元素类型和你显能的类型相同。\n你可以用以下方式增强此技能：\n1、每额外消耗1灵能点，该能力增加一个伤害骰。\n2、如果在该能力显能时消耗了灵能集中，该能力消耗减少1（最小0），但是伤害也会减少1d3且无法进一步提升。"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EntanglingEctoplasm.Name",
    "enGB_Base": "Entangling Ectoplasm",
    "zhCN": "纠缠灵质"
  },
  {
    "Key": "EntanglingEctoplasm.Description",
    "enGB_Base": "You draw forth a glob of ectoplasmic goo from the Astral Plane and immediately throw it as a ranged touch attack at any creature in range. On a successful hit, the subject is covered in goo and becomes entangled. The goo evaporates at the end of the power’s duration. Entangled creatures can attempt to break free as a move action, making a Strength or Escape Artist check. The DC for this check is equal to 11 + the manifester’s key ability modifier.\nFor every 2 additional power points you spend, this power’s save DC increases by 1",
    "zhCN": "你从星界抽出一团灵质粘液，并立即将其作为远程接触攻击扔向范围内的任何生物。成功击中后，对象会被粘液覆盖并被缠住。粘稠物会在能量持续时间结束时蒸发。被纠缠的生物可以通过一个移动动作尝试挣脱，进行力量或或灵巧检定检定。该检定的 DC 等于 11 + 显能者的主要能力调整值。\n。每额外消耗2灵能点，该能力的豁免DC就会增加1。" },
  ]
